          <!-- Written by → author photo: masked by the black box but NOT moving with it.
               The group counter-translates against the box's slide (same frames + easing),
               so these stay fixed on the canvas and the box's top edge reveals them. -->
          <div class="t2-authorgroup">
            <div class="t2-writtenby" data-editable data-name="Written by" contenteditable="true">WRITTEN BY</div>
